<title>Storyboard 1 — Karim — RecallIt</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  body { font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif; background:#0d0d0d; color:#f5f0e8; }
  h1,h2 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; }
  .mono { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; }
  .top-bar { background:#111; border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a2a; padding:10px 0; font-size:0.8rem; }
  .top-bar a { color:#c9a84c; text-decoration:none; }
  .top-bar a:hover { color:#f5f0e8; }
  .label { font-size:0.72rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.15em; color:#c9a84c; font-weight:600; }
  .persona-card { background:#1a1a1a; border-left:3px solid #c9a84c; padding:22px 24px; margin-bottom:32px; }
  .persona-card h5 { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; color:#c9a84c; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .persona-card li,.persona-card p { font-size:0.88rem; color:#bbb; }
  .step-label { font-size:0.7rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.12em; color:#c9a84c; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .step-card { background:#1a1a1a; border:1px solid #2a2a2a; height:100%; }
  .mockup { background:#0d0d0d; padding:18px; min-height:230px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
  .caption { padding:16px 18px; }
  .caption h6 { font-weight:600; margin-bottom:4px; font-size:0.92rem; }
  .caption p { font-size:0.82rem; color:#999; margin:0; }
  .arrow { color:#c9a84c; font-size:1.4rem; text-align:center; padding-top:90px; }
  .bottom-links { font-size:0.82rem; border-top:1px solid #2a2a2a; padding-top:20px; margin-top:40px; display:flex; gap:28px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .bottom-links a { text-decoration:none; }

  /* mockup pieces - arcade style */
  .mn { background:#000; height:26px; border-radius:2px; margin-bottom:10px; display:flex; align-items:center; padding:0 10px; }
  .mn-logo { font-size:0.62rem; color:#c9a84c; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.05em; }
  .mn-link { font-size:0.58rem; color:#666; margin-left:auto; }
  .level-pill { display:inline-block; background:#1a1a1a; border:1px solid #333; border-radius:20px; padding:5px 14px; font-size:0.62rem; margin:3px; color:#999; }
  .level-pill.active { background:#1a6b3a; border-color:#1a6b3a; color:#fff; }
  .len-grid { display:flex; gap:6px; margin-top:8px; }
  .len-box { flex:1; height:32px; background:#1a1a1a; border:1px solid #333; border-radius:3px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:0.68rem; color:#888; }
  .len-box.active { background:#c9a84c; color:#000; border-color:#c9a84c; font-weight:700; }
  .digit-row { display:flex; gap:8px; justify-content:center; margin:18px 0; }
  .digit-box { width:34px; height:42px; background:#1a1a1a; border:2px solid #1a6b3a; border-radius:4px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:1.2rem; font-weight:700; color:#1a6b3a; }
  .digit-box.dim { border-color:#333; color:#444; }
  .digit-box.typed { border-color:#c9a84c; color:#f5f0e8; }
  .digit-box.empty { border-color:#333; background:transparent; }
  .timer-bar { height:4px; background:#1a1a1a; border-radius:2px; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .timer-fill { height:100%; width:60%; background:#1a6b3a; }
  .score-row { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:0.65rem; color:#888; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .score-row b { color:#c9a84c; }
  .result-big { text-align:center; padding:20px 0; }
  .result-big .num { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:2.2rem; font-weight:700; color:#1a6b3a; }
  .result-big .lbl { font-size:0.65rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.1em; color:#888; }
  .btn-mock { background:#1a6b3a; border-radius:3px; padding:8px; text-align:center; font-size:0.68rem; color:#fff; font-weight:600; margin-top:auto; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="top-bar">
  <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between">
    <a href="../index.html">&larr; Portfolio</a>
    <span style="color:#555;">Assignment 3 — Storyboard 1 of 2</span>
    <a href="memorygame-storyboard2.html">Storyboard 2 &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container py-5">
  <p class="label">SEG3125 — Assignment 3 — RecallIt</p>
  <h1 style="font-size:2.2rem; margin-bottom:6px;">Storyboard 1 — Karim</h1>
  <p style="color:#888; font-size:0.9rem; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Dark arcade theme &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Score-driven, competitive pacing</p>

  <div class="persona-card">
    <h5>Karim, 21 — University Student</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Competitive — wants a high score and a reason to immediately replay</li>
      <li>Tech-savvy, plays casual games on his phone between classes</li>
      <li>Short attention span — wants the setup to take seconds, not minutes</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin:0;"><strong style="color:#f5f0e8;">Goal:</strong> Beat his own best score by recalling longer digit sequences, fast.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row g-3">
    <div class="col-md-3 col-10 mx-auto mx-md-0">
      <p class="step-label">Step 01 — Setup</p>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mn"><span class="mn-logo">RECALLIT</span><span class="mn-link">Best: 8</span></div>
          <p style="font-size:0.65rem; color:#666; margin-bottom:6px;">SELECT LEVEL</p>
          <div><span class="level-pill">Easy</span><span class="level-pill active">Pro</span><span class="level-pill">Expert</span></div>
          <p style="font-size:0.65rem; color:#666; margin:10px 0 4px;">SEQUENCE LENGTH</p>
          <div class="len-grid">
            <div class="len-box">4</div><div class="len-box active">6</div><div class="len-box">8</div><div class="len-box">10</div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn-mock">START</div>
        </div>
        <div class="caption"><h6>Picks Pro / length 6</h6><p>Karim taps through level pills and a length grid — two taps, no menus to dig through.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-1 d-none d-md-block arrow">&rarr;</div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-10 mx-auto mx-md-0">
      <p class="step-label">Step 02 — Memorize</p>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mn"><span class="mn-logo">RECALLIT</span></div>
          <div class="timer-bar"><div class="timer-fill"></div></div>
          <p style="font-size:0.62rem; color:#666; text-align:center; margin-bottom:10px;">MEMORIZE THE SEQUENCE</p>
          <div class="digit-row">
            <div class="digit-box">7</div>
            <div class="digit-box dim">3</div>
            <div class="digit-box dim">9</div>
            <div class="digit-box dim">1</div>
            <div class="digit-box dim">5</div>
            <div class="digit-box dim">2</div>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size:0.6rem; color:#444; text-align:center;">Digits flash one at a time</p>
        </div>
        <div class="caption"><h6>Digits flash in sequence</h6><p>One digit lights up at a time against a near-black field — high contrast keeps focus on the active digit.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-1 d-none d-md-block arrow">&rarr;</div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-10 mx-auto mx-md-0">
      <p class="step-label">Step 02b — Recall</p>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mn"><span class="mn-logo">RECALLIT</span></div>
          <p style="font-size:0.62rem; color:#666; text-align:center; margin-bottom:10px;">TYPE WHAT YOU SAW</p>
          <div class="digit-row">
            <div class="digit-box typed">7</div>
            <div class="digit-box typed">3</div>
            <div class="digit-box typed">9</div>
            <div class="digit-box empty"></div>
            <div class="digit-box empty"></div>
            <div class="digit-box empty"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="score-row"><span>Streak: <b>4</b></span><span>Time left: <b>3s</b></span></div>
          <div class="btn-mock">SUBMIT</div>
        </div>
        <div class="caption"><h6>Types the sequence back</h6><p>A live streak counter and countdown keep the pressure on — feedback Karim wants while racing the clock.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-1 d-none d-md-block arrow">&rarr;</div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-10 mx-auto mx-md-0">
      <p class="step-label">Step 03 — Result</p>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mn"><span class="mn-logo">RECALLIT</span></div>
          <div class="result-big">
            <div class="num">NEW BEST</div>
            <p style="font-size:0.65rem; color:#888; margin:6px 0;">Sequence length</p>
            <div class="num" style="font-size:2.6rem;">9</div>
            <div class="lbl">DIGITS RECALLED</div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn-mock">PLAY AGAIN</div>
        </div>
        <div class="caption"><h6>Sees new high score</h6><p>Big bold number and an immediate "Play Again" button — built for the replay loop Karim is after.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom-links">
    <a href="../memory-game/index.html" style="color:#c9a84c;">View High-Fidelity Prototype &rarr;</a>
    <a href="memorygame-storyboard2.html" style="color:#666;">Storyboard 2 &rarr;</a>
    <a href="../index.html" style="color:#666;">Portfolio &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
